{"tid":1637721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】救護員疑戴口罩放工被捕 警掩分局搜查 拒答警員編號　","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:52:06.000Z","uid":29625,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65f13edad0699947f4fef64e913162c7181fa10f","tid":1637721,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"蒙面惡法生效後，警權進一步澎脹，有讀者向本報爆料指，一名隸屬荃灣局的救護員，前日收工，在元朗巴士途中，被警員截查，並因為他戴口罩而將他拘捕。警方事後更到所屬消防區搜索。<span style=\"color: red;\">消防處救護員會承認事件屬實</span>，正密切跟進中。<br />\n<br />\n讀者本身也是救護員，他指前日（周日）有同袍因戴口罩搭巴士而被捕。<span style=\"color: red;\">翌日警方進入局內搜查該同事儲物櫃，當時局長叫同事記下警員姓名、編號及駐守單位，卻換來極不禮貌一句「我都未做嘢，你問咩呀」。最後也拒絕提供，只肯以傳真後補。</span><br />\n<br />\n讀者稱，被捕的救護員當晚7時37分收工，至晚上8時多返到元朗落車。當時元朗還有零星的衝突，而<span style=\"color: red;\">該同事據悉因為身體不適而戴口罩</span>，結果被防暴警拘捕。讀者續稱，警方到分局搜查時，<span style=\"color: red;\">局長本來放假，也專程返回了解，要求警員提供資料，卻指他們阻差辦公。</span><br />\n<br />\n據知，該<span style=\"color: orange;\">救護員被扣查中，律師及家屬都未能與其本人接觸。</span><br />\n<br />\n消防處救護員會主席李偉孝接受本報查詢時承認事件，並說：「有理事接觸過當時人，而我在等回覆中，未交談過，要了解所有內容再回應。」<br />\n<br />\n就休班救護員戴口罩被捕一事，本報正向消防處及警方查詢。"},{"pid":"f4c215b2650b38853031ebee4e79cc168c2c2d6d","tid":1637721,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"蘋果已FC<br />\n黑警好撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a67bfa30c9741f88e7aa4437a005708939ecb5c","tid":1637721,"uid":195350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3560c50a3937646bbe3977b68bd772784d7a2ae8","tid":1637721,"uid":83283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"CLS 推！"},{"pid":"c6ff0cdd8c7a04ea60e0a38a212ac04e9c20ed1d","tid":1637721,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"五大部隊撐匪犬，係唔包救護員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28861120791387f1001dddbb2d3059ea497ba4d6","tid":1637721,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"原爆料post<br />\n<br />\npopo又一傑作 拉左個病戴口罩嘅救護！！同我推！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajxaDmU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajxaDmU</a>"},{"pid":"fa3b2badc84c54f7d3ab22c81c192da2008e596e","tid":1637721,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5096402e8f13201803f4b356ac40535d3ee9f568","tid":1637721,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h